141
00:15:10,254 --> 00:15:12,456
Canadian, even.

142
00:15:12,556 --> 00:15:14,792
What do I need to do?

143
00:15:14,892 --> 00:15:17,258
Oh, I took care of it.

144
00:15:17,994 --> 00:15:21,830
