156
00:16:21,756 --> 00:16:24,977
Well, Derby.
Ain't you become ever so handsome.

157
00:16:25,227 --> 00:16:26,731
What can I do you for?

158
00:16:27,764 --> 00:16:29,577
I'm...

159
00:16:30,801 --> 00:16:33,036
waiting on a parcel.

160
00:16:33,135 --> 00:16:38,038
You ain't heard? They murdered the mailman.
Out there on Highway 358.

161
00:16:39,942 --> 00:16:41,298
Where's the mail?

162
