from the nation's capital to give it to me.

184
00:19:14,096 --> 00:19:17,198
Wow. How much?

185
00:19:17,967 --> 00:19:19,701
A lifetime sum.

186
00:19:21,369 --> 00:19:22,436
Shit.

187
