Bank pageant.

188
00:19:55,270 --> 00:19:57,840
- Right.
- Hey! I'm gonna win it.

189
00:19:57,941 --> 00:20:01,077
And we're gonna need those $5,000
to make our new life in Butte.

190
00:20:01,178 --> 00:20:03,211
- Butte?
- Yeah!

191
00:20:03,746 --> 00:20:06,048
Don't sell yourself short, hummingbird.

192
00:20:06,148 --> 00:20:08,451
The money I'm getting,
we're moving to California.

193
00:20:08,852 --> 00:20:12,388
- California?
- Yeah. I'll start my own body shop.

194
00:20:12,489 --> 00:20:14,857
Ain't like startin' a business
is easy, dummy.

195
00:20:14,958 --> 00:20:17,861
Hey, I'm good for it. May not know
how they do in the city yet,

196
00:20:17,961 --> 00:20:20,563
but I sure as hell know how to fix cars.

197
00:20:20,663 --> 00:20:22,398
You want me workin' for your daddy
the rest of our lives?

198
00:20:22,499 --> 00:20:24,500
No way.

199
00:20:41,717 --> 00:20:44,320
You know I'll take care of you.

200
00:20:45,887 --> 00:20:47,523
And do whatever it takes.

201
00:20:47,874 --> 00:20:49,723
Yeah.

202
00:20:50,659 --> 00:20:53,730
- I'm proud of you.
- I know.

203
00:20:53,829 --> 00:20:57,396
Me and Miss Cut Bank, chasin' it.

204
